{"tid":2270502,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"休班警去年商場拍攝遭私了 今供稱示威者當日嗌「佔中」口號","createTime":"2020-11-04T05:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T06:28:03.000Z","uid":5195,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a743a76f8c71c93e8df864a63776079ef2198b55","tid":2270502,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:12:38.000Z","msg":"休班警去年9月在屯門市廣場疑因舉機拍攝示威者唱歌而遭「私了」，涉案地盤工及男生就傷人及非法集結兩罪受審。案中休班警今出庭作供，指當日商場中庭有人大叫「佔中」口號，他欲用手機拍片並放上網，「等人知呢度情景」；惟突然身後有人質問他，並向中庭的人大叫：「呢度有黑警影緊你哋相！」他繼而遭一群年輕人包圍指罵及毆打。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/IPOS4G6NQZCJ3PYKXZLDLXH6X4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2FIPOS4G6NQZCJ3PYKXZLDLXH6X4%2F&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3Vcyo429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=2b1570c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201104%2FIPOS4G6NQZCJ3PYKXZLDLXH6X4%2F&h=cbb07383\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201104/IPOS4G6NQZCJ3PYKXZLDLXH6X4/</a>"},{"pid":"3b4bd6b3a845f6eaeeac50e310734435bb866d42","tid":2270502,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"佔領中南海⁉"},{"pid":"2c3695f19459d7583d7c2a68c181b71e982a9b2f","tid":2270502,"uid":7125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"無人想佔領中国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794825dd331fcaa619be7ad9fa0627e57fa09cea","tid":2270502,"uid":226421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"一日最衰都係佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9521ae2ef03f8d481ac11b39c921077244dc8c13","tid":2270502,"uid":44718,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T06:23:47.000Z","msg":"佔中口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"